{"tid":759413,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(軍事撚請入，求指教)如果美國佬向全世界宣戰，佢夠唔夠抽？","createTime":"2018-07-28T14:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T15:26:13.000Z","uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a19df185f0b1211e2ccdc1e63787e9c98c52618a","tid":759413,"uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"聞說現今世界有空軍就已經贏一半，美國坐擁嘅空軍多到不得了，中國加埋俄羅斯都唔夠佢多。<br />\n如果全世界vs美國，美國佬贏唔贏到？<br />\n<br />\n地理上，俄羅斯大量嘅陸軍又唔可以進攻歐洲咁地面推進，同啲強嘅軍事國又隔咗個海。<br />\n<br />\n美國又多核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求軍事撚指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f99bc1304acf6d4b540870b4ab9a3f3e0ee17d","tid":759413,"uid":123034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc37ab2d8bfbf4491a15349ed0344df428b8340","tid":759413,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"肯定唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實打仗咪係燒錢<br />\n一個國家邊夠全世界燒啊<br />\n淨係打亞洲都唔夠打(計埋俄佬)"},{"pid":"dee6f393b223c9bb45367600e9089e681da485a2","tid":759413,"uid":58247,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"睇你因咩事打仗 <br />\n無原因就單挑全世界既話真係無乜可能贏"},{"pid":"c562e015ffa7267bd502fc2bb662a5a543aa7b05","tid":759413,"uid":2720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"假設係常規戰 加拿大併入美國 冇反戰撚 咁應該就算唔贏都夠唔輸"},{"pid":"151119dc501c223a9dc9f2e8257cf78616864169","tid":759413,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a876c5ee09227f6455bdf55ff65b8183b748f8c5","tid":759413,"uid":57148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T22:03:02.000Z","msg":"唔好以為多核彈就會用啦好嘛<br />\n<br />\nStability-instability pa